data.description: Be captivated by the mid-century vibe. Living room offers vaulted ceilings, that exudes a sense of space & light that is both inviting & calming. Bask in the warm glow of the natural fireplace. Family room offers built-ins for all your heirlooms. First floor laundry & the owner's bedroom is a tranquil retreat with its own en-suite bathroom. The home boasts a beautiful & private yard, perfect for gatherings or simply enjoying the natural beauty that surrounds you. The patio or sun porch is an ideal spot for morning coffee or evening cocktails. This is being sold in AS-IS condition. Photos have been enhanced. Electric has been updated!
